body:
Is there possibly a way you can make it to when I get an error from YOUR game like "failed to create dump file" it doesn't give us a penalty?? I don't know how many times this has happened to me and it irritates me to no extent. I'm getting penalized for no reason because this dump file, and probably along with many other summoners. I've never had this problem until recently-the past 2 months.

So, is there a way the client can recognize this and not give a penalty? {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}

Edit: I'm playing ranked too. So..
